<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 28 Nov 2024 06:22:02 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>日产 10 月份全球产量下降（墨西哥除外），但特朗普关税威胁迫在眉睫</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/nissan-october-production-down-globally-except-mexico-trump-tariff-threat-looms-2024-11-28/</link><description>日产汽车周四表示，10 月份全球产量连续第五个月下降，主要是由于除墨西哥以外的大多数制造中心产量下降。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Nov 2024 06:06:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/nissan-october-production-down-globally-except-mexico-trump-tariff-threat-looms-2024-11-28/</guid></item><item><title>丰田10月份全球产量连续第九个月下降</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/toyotas-global-output-declines-ninth-straight-month-october-2024-11-28/</link><description>受美国和中国产量大幅下降的拖累，丰田汽车10月份全球产量连续第九个月下降，但与前几个月相比，降幅较温和。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Nov 2024 04:38:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/toyotas-global-output-declines-ninth-straight-month-october-2024-11-28/</guid></item><item><title>由于担心新的贸易战，中国官方媒体赞扬了一些美国公司</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/chinas-state-media-praise-some-us-firms-amid-fears-new-trade-war-2024-11-28/</link><description>中国官方媒体赞扬一些美国公司的“强有力合作”——这种评论是在担心贸易战的情况下发表的，让人想起唐纳德·特朗普(Donald Trump)担任第一任总统期间中国报纸如何报道中美紧张局势。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Nov 2024 02:31:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/chinas-state-media-praise-some-us-firms-amid-fears-new-trade-war-2024-11-28/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲股市低迷，美元在美国感恩节前波动</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-11-28/</link><description>周四亚洲股市低迷，美元处于守势，此前美国数据显示，尽管经济仍保持弹性，但通胀放缓的进展却陷入停滞，引发了人们对美联储明年可能采取的政策的怀疑。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Nov 2024 02:21:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-11-28/</guid></item><item><title>台湾在总统太平洋之行前举行防空演习</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-holds-air-defence-drill-ahead-presidents-pacific-trip-2024-11-28/</link><description>台湾军方周四清晨举行了一次防空演习，以测试其反应和交战程序，随后台湾总统赖清德将于本周末前往太平洋，其中包括美国中途停留。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Nov 2024 00:30:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-holds-air-defence-drill-ahead-presidents-pacific-trip-2024-11-28/</guid></item><item><title>中国科学家争先恐后地开发耐气候马铃薯</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-scientists-rush-climate-proof-potatoes-2024-11-27/</link><description>在北京西北部的一个研究机构中，分子生物学家李杰平和他的团队从盆栽植物中收获了七颗异常小的土豆，其中一颗只有鹌鹑蛋那么小。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 23:13:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-scientists-rush-climate-proof-potatoes-2024-11-27/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：由于关税谈判给市场蒙上阴影，科技股拖累美国股指走低</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphics-2024-11-27/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 21:51:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphics-2024-11-27/</guid></item><item><title>特朗普可能会在关税攻势中转向经过考验的贸易法工具</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/trump-likely-turn-tested-trade-law-tools-his-tariff-offensive-2024-11-27/</link><description>人们普遍预计，美国当选总统唐纳德·特朗普将再次诉诸最喜欢的法律工具，以支持对墨西哥、加拿大和中国进口商品征收关税的威胁：《国际紧急经济权力法案》，这是实施其更广泛关税议程的几个法律途径之一。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 18:21:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/trump-likely-turn-tested-trade-law-tools-his-tariff-offensive-2024-11-27/</guid></item><item><title>特朗普对关税下了高风险、高回报的赌注，以遏制芬太尼</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/trump-places-high-risk-high-reward-bet-tariffs-stem-fentanyl-2024-11-27/</link><description>专家表示，美国当选总统唐纳德·特朗普誓言要对中国和墨西哥征收关税，除非它们阻止芬太尼和移民越过美国边境流动，这可能会促使这些国家政府在缉毒警务方面进行更深入的合作。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 16:46:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/trump-places-high-risk-high-reward-bet-tariffs-stem-fentanyl-2024-11-27/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟国家支持对中国钛白粉征收关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/eu-countries-back-duties-chinese-titanium-dioxide-2024-11-27/</link><description>据了解欧盟调查情况的消息人士透露，欧盟成员国周三为欧盟对从中国进口的二氧化钛（TiO2）征收明确的反倾销税扫清了道路。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 15:13:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/eu-countries-back-duties-chinese-titanium-dioxide-2024-11-27/</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯表示如果美国在日本部署导弹俄罗斯将做出回应</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/russia-says-it-will-respond-if-us-places-missiles-japan-2024-11-27/</link><description>俄罗斯周三表示，如果美国在日本部署导弹，这将威胁俄罗斯的安全，并促使莫斯科采取报复行动。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 14:35:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/russia-says-it-will-respond-if-us-places-missiles-japan-2024-11-27/</guid></item><item><title>经过多年的外交努力，中国释放了三名美国公民</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-brokers-release-three-americans-imprisoned-china-politico-reports-2024-11-27/</link><description>白宫周三表示，中国已经释放了美国公民马克·斯维丹(Mark Swidan)、李凯(Kai Li)和梁约翰(John Leung)，结束了多年来针对华盛顿称在中国被错误拘留的美国人的外交努力。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 13:55:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-brokers-release-three-americans-imprisoned-china-politico-reports-2024-11-27/</guid></item><item><title>宜家高管表示，贸易关税使保持低价变得更加困难</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/trade-tariffs-make-it-harder-keep-prices-low-ikea-executive-says-2024-11-27/</link><description>全球最大家具零售商首席财务官周三对路透社表示，美国当选总统唐纳德·特朗普计划的关税将使宜家更难保持低价。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 13:04:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/trade-tariffs-make-it-harder-keep-prices-low-ikea-executive-says-2024-11-27/</guid></item><item><title>预言家阿萨尼击中制胜球，光州队在亚冠联赛中保持第二名</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/prophetic-asani-hits-winner-gwangju-stay-second-asian-champions-league-2024-11-27/</link><description>替补出场的贾西尔·阿萨尼首次触球得分，帮助光州足球俱乐部以 1-0 战胜上海申花队，横滨水手队击败浦项制铁队，帮助韩国队在亚冠精英联赛阶段保持第二名。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 12:46:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/prophetic-asani-hits-winner-gwangju-stay-second-asian-champions-league-2024-11-27/</guid></item><item><title>德国为中国企业提供更多投资担保</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/germany-issues-more-investment-guarantees-business-china-2024-11-27/</link><description>德国经济部的数据显示，德国政府对华投资的国家担保价值在经历大幅下降后，今年有所上升。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 11:42:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/germany-issues-more-investment-guarantees-business-china-2024-11-27/</guid></item></channel></rss>